## üìÑ Use the Pull Request Template

- Use the official template located at [pull_request_template.md](mdc:.github/PULL_REQUEST_TEMPLATE/pull_request_template.md)
- Fill out each section accurately:
  - **Description**: Brief summary of the change. Include the issue it addresses using `Fixes #123`
  - **Type of Change**: Check the relevant options (e.g., bug fix, feature, breaking change)
  - **Testing**: Explain how the change was tested or verified
  - **Checklist**: Mark all completed items
  - **Optional Sections**: Add screenshots or context as needed

