## ‚úÖ Best Practices

- Use clear, descriptive PR titles starting with a tag, e.g., `[BUG]`, `[FEATURE]`
- Always link relevant issues using `Fixes #issue-number` to enable auto-closing
- Ensure all CI tests pass before submitting
- Do **not** mix unrelated changes in a single PR
